            "tips": "Opposite: mature. Not the same as 'young' (age) vs. 'immature' (behavior inappropriate for age). Often used as criticism: 'That was immature of you.'"
        },
        {
            "word": "opportunity",
            "wordType": "noun",
            "definition": [
                {
